{
  "stem": "4753.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody really thought about things what really happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was rumors that we will be sent-- my father, mother, and my little brother, and a few other people, naturally-- to a separate camp directly to Germany because we were a special group, because my father was in the First World War, and he was a hero in the war.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because my brother was in the army in that time also-- in 1944, also still.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a privileged group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was the things we were talking about-- the plan and how and where we really will go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they put us into the railroad car, and we did go quite a bit to a direction, they came to the conclusion they made a mistake, and sent our train to the opposite way than they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's the way we came to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you go anywhere after you were in the brick factory?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the brick factory, we were divided-- I think that was the time-- to go 50 people to homes-- oh, I am sorry-- homes what was owned by Jews, and they called them ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were there also a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then from there, we were taken to the-- walked-- to the railroad station and taken to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were walls in the rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were smaller group of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were 50 people instead of 2,000 together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was maybe more bearable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then there were the problems-- people who were not Jewish, just one of their grandparents were Jewish, and because of that, they had to come to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
